body.description: Product Description Energizer N Batteries deliver reliable power to your important electronics. These E90 batteries are great camera batteries, and they're compatible with a variety of other devices, including bluetooth headsets and video game controllers. Ideal for medical equipment, Energizer N batteries work in a variety of blood pressure monitors and glucose monitors. Energizer miniature alkaline batteries contain zero mercury, giving you a responsible battery option that minimizes environmental impact. Count on Energizer, the #1 brand of specialty batteries, to deliver long lasting power to your devices. Amazon.com Energizer Max BatteriesEnergizer Max batteries provide long-lasting dependable power for your everyday devices.
